Subject: drm/amdgpu: split gfx_v9_0_kiq_init_queue into two
Git-commit: 898b7893e43ea47f4953bf61bd57802c33337c11
Patch-mainline: v4.13-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

One for KIQ and one for the KCQ. This simplifies the logic and
allows for future optimizations.

